    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Berlin Marquette County Wis-<lb/>consin</placeName>
                <date>July 23<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1854</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Editor Occident</p>
            <p>Sir! Enclosed find Three Dollars<lb/> in payment for the Occident till<lb/> next
                    <date>March</date></p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">Yours</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">
                <persName role="author">M. Markwell</persName>
            </p>
            <p/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir as I am not more<lb/> a citizen of <placeName>Yazoo City
                    Mississippi</placeName> and<lb/> have no place of <sic>Resident</sic> at
                present<lb/> you will be so kind to stop of sending<lb/> to your Boock<add>?</add>
                the Occident and as I<lb/>
                <sic>belive</sic> that my year is very near over<lb/> also have you gand<add>?</add>
                those <add>Hebrew</add> according<lb/> to the german &amp; Polish minhag if you<lb/>
                have I shall want one or two setts also<lb/> I should like to have a
                    <add>Hebrew</add> with Hebrew<lb/> &amp; English Dear Sir I am Respectfully
                yours</p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">
                <persName role="author">Levi M. Lavenberg</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
    </text>
